  "description": "The neon-tetra half of the duet. Bright soprano formant, high partial emphasis, fast vibrato at 7 Hz — feliX's signature nervous energy rendered as vocal shimmer. Effort 0.7 pushes into belt territory where feliX is most alive. Drama at 0.5 keeps partials dancing at the edge of synchrony — chaotic enough to sparkle, ordered enough to sing. Pair with Oscar Hums for the full OddfeliX/OddOscar experience.",
